query:
SELECT 
  i.id as intakeId,
  i.status,
  i.previewToken,
  i.previewUrl,
  e.id as emailLogId,
  e.emailType,
  e.sentAt
FROM intakes i
LEFT JOIN email_logs e ON i.id = e.intakeId AND e.emailType = 'ready_for_review'
WHERE i.email = 'e2e-test-jan5@launchbase-test.com'
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC, e.sentAt DESC
LIMIT 1;
